 * 'Shadow Cat and Snow Tech Walked around the base a
bit but they never found anyone. Snow Tech was getting
anoyed and frustrated. He decided to listen in on them
via his com-link. After opening his com-link he and
Shadow Cat heard Dark Mouses Request for help, but
didn't hear a reply. Shadow Cat looked at Snow Tech.*

 " We should help if no one else will, I mean, we
can't just let an injured bot lie there!"

 * Snow Tech nodded,*

 " Yeah, the service around here is crappy, so we
might as well do something to pass the time while
Inny, Er, has her fun."

 * And so, with that agreement, they headed for the
signal, which was dangerously close to the Predacon
base.*
